Question: One image shows one primarily yellow train headed leftward, and the other image shows on primarily red train headed rightward.

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a primarily yellow train headed leftward?')

ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a primarily red train headed rightward?')

ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} xor {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
